{"id": "1394575126577807411", "channel_id": "1394575126577807411", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "每个人都有最美味的部位：记者的声带、政治家的舌头、舞者的腓肠肌…\n\n但，无法满足啊~残月如何与满月媲美？\n渴望一具完美的肉身！一具像「杜勒赛因」般的至美珍馐：\n「杜勒赛因」注视着自己被吞咽的遗体，一种前所未有的美妙滋味自共感味蕾传来——哈，真想全部吃掉！\n\n疯狂的进食正以饥饿的名义汹涌而至：*“你也对我的味道感到渴望吗，守密人阁下？”*\n\n——✦——✦—— ✦✦✦ ——✦——✦——\n\nEveryone has their most delicious part: a journalist’s vocal cord, a politician’s tongue, a dancer’s calves… but such small morsels only serve to highlight the void. A waning moon cannot compare to the full.\n\nHe craves a truly perfect body, a peerless delicacy! One such as *Doresain's*—he once consumed his own remains, and as he savored the unprecedented flavor, Doresain found himself overwhelmed by a truly delicious insight. Yes, indeed, to taste perfection, one must simply turn the gaze inward.\n\nHunger is the only master worth serving. *\"Do you, too, crave the taste of my flesh, dear Keeper?\"*", "timestamp": "2025-07-15T07:03:40.129000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-07-15T07:04:24.187000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "wish", "emoji_id": "1356084702468899117", "count": 23}, {"emoji": "🐓", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}, {"emoji": "🚫", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}, {"emoji": "perfect", "emoji_id": "1356084498630053979", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "chefs_kiss", "emoji_id": "988672059439722546", "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1394575128209260676", "filename": "1-.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 9216966, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1394575126577807411/1394575128209260676/1-.jpg?ex=69ccc34c&is=69cb71cc&hm=053d5b8ff1ac7965609e08bbd216eca85a3ad8a6b2481b7b69db5a6646cf0a00&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1394575126577807411", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.3 杜勒赛因情报：进食┊V2.3 About Doresain: The Epicure", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["135726795790195108